STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Donald J. ROGERS, Defendant-Petitioner. M-991/992 September Term 2017
080500 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 4, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motions of the American Civil Liberties Union of New Jersey for leave to file a motion for leave to appear as amicus curiae as within time (M-991) and to file a brief as amicus curiae (M-992) are granted.
